Intel(R) Parallel Studio XE 2015 tool
suite simplifies the design,
development, debug, and tuning of code
that utilizes parallel processing to
boost application performance. Get
more application performance with less
effort on compatible Intel(R)
processors and coprocessors.

This is the complete Studio Suite also
called Cluster Edition:

- compilers, performance libraries,
and parallel models optimized to build
fast parallel code.
- performance profiler, threading
design/prototyping, and memory &
thread debugger to design, build,
debug and tune fast parallel code.
- a MPI cluster communications
library, along with MPI error checking
and tuning to design,
build, debug and tune fast parallel
code that includes MPI.

Have fun coding!
